09/06/2003
ZADAR, Croatia -- A regional conference of environment ministers from the 17 countries in the Adriatic-Ionian Initiative took place in Croatia on Friday (6 June). 
The event ended with the adoption of an action plan for environmental protection of the Adriatic, as well as a memorandum of understanding for a $12m project to protect the Neretva River delta. 
(Media Scan, Beta - 09/06/03; Onasa - 08/06/03)
